column5: I know it's late for a lot of you, early for some of you, but either way, Have a super day and be safe doing the life thing.
Good morning Roy.  Hi Ho   Hi Ho .... It's off to work I go.
Any morning I wake up and there is no chalk line around me is off to a super start LOL.  You have a super day one and all!
That's it Roy.......Make them all memorable........LOL@ Big Cliff..............TC all and Tight lines.....Chuck.............
Alright if Roy ain't going to be the crumugin then I will " bah humbug" stupid sunny 80F degree day.   Art

Morning to you too Roy.  I'm stuck at work here, but oh well...gotta make money for fishing stuff right?  Art...LOL at your 80 degree day...thunderstorms here today and snow by Thursday...jeez...gotta love Canada....
Good morning! Last nice day here for a while! Snow? Keep that stuff on the other side of the lake! LOL
Sheesh someone who gets up before Lew.I didn't know there were cows to milk on your farm in Boucherville.
Oh I see the times just changed on the computer your post went from 4:34am to 5:34am.
Good Morning everyone,.. Just realized, 57 days till my fly-in trip with cochrane air services??

Good morning to you  Roy and everyone else. Good to see so many going to work......ensures my Pension for another Month Every day is a good one as long as I'm looking at the grass from the green side!!!
Good Morning All,  Have a super great day!  Cheers,  Jen
Am I too late to say good morn,n to ya,no matter,have a great day.
Good morning Snookums.  Have a great day!!!  Good one Cliff    Now I'm laughing this morning  Joey
